Package drawnet.lib.filters

Class Summary
Filter Superclass of import/export filters.
FilterData This is a abstract class to derive from if you need a class to store filter's data.
FilterDataGSPN A class to store GSPN filter's data.
FilterDataGSPNSta A class to store GSPNSta filter's data.
FilterDataOsMoSysIn This class is an abstraction for an rsl OsMoSys file.
FilterDataOsMoSysIn_Old This class is an abstraction for an rsl OsMoSys file.
FilterUtils  
FormulaFilter Class to import FT formula.
GSPNFilter The Filter allows to export a model in the format used by GSPN.
GSPNStaFilter A Filter to import GreatSPN .sta files.
OsMoSysFormalismOutFilter Class to export formalisms in OsMoSys format.
OsMoSysInFilter Class to import OsMoSys results.
OsMoSysInFilter_Old Class to import OsMoSys results.
OsMoSysOutFilter Exports models in OsMoSys format.
PlanesOutFilter Exports models in XML format, filtering on planes.
PnmlOutFilter Exports models in PNML format using PNML Framework (http://move.lip6.fr/PNML/index.html).
TransientFilter Class to import FT transient results.
XMLFilter Superclass of import/export XML filters.
XMLFormalismFilter A filter to read/write formalisms in XML format.
XMLModelFilter A filter to read/write models in XML format (current format).
